GxClientModels

    Package Description
    GxClientModels
    The package exports a collection of classes which describe the client models in BBj.

    Class and Description
    GxClientAddRangeSelectionModel
    The model is used to compose a range selection model in order to be applied on the client.
    GxClientColumnModel

    GxClientFilterAbstractModel
    A generic abstract implementation for the GxClientFilterModel interface
    GxClientFilterModel

    GxClientFilterSimpleModel

    GxClientRowModel
